os.rename(renamed a file)
os.getcwd(current dir you use)
os.getmtime(get modified time file)
os.getsize(get size of file)
os.mkdir(create a dir)
os.chdir(setwd in R -- change dir)
os.rmdir (remove dir, but just if it's empty - no contents)
os.path.getabspath(get absolut path)

how to check contents in dir?

os.listdir -- returns list of all the files

os.path.join() -- create a full path and check if one of list itens identified is a dir too

